OL,6,FHitman Kenneth Eugene Smith became the
OL,7,Ffirst person to be put to death using
OL,8,Fpure nitrogen gas - a punishment he
OL,9,Fargued it was a 'cruel' and 'unusual'
OL,10,Fas Ian Woods reports
OL,12,FA man who was paid $1,000 (#788) to
OL,13,Fkill an Alabama woman more than 30
OL,14,Fyears ago was executed with pure
OL,15,Fnitrogen gas - the first execution of
OL,16,Fits kind in the world.
OL,18,FConvicted murderer Kenneth Smith, 58,
OL,19,Fappeared to convulse and shake after
OL,20,Fbreathing in the gas.
