OL,6,FFor at least two minutes, Smith made
OL,7,Fseizure-like movements on the gurney
OL,8,Fthat sometimes had him pulling against
OL,9,Fthe restraints.
OL,11,FThat was followed by several minutes
OL,12,Fof laboured breathing. He was
OL,13,Fpronounced dead after 22 minutes.
OL,15,FInside the chamber with him was his
OL,16,Fspiritual adviser, Revered Jeff Hood
